Adding  Indicators (arrows):  The measures for the KPI Arrows and colors are in Step 9 but see below again:


KPI AVG Arrow = SWITCH(TRUE(), [Avg. Price] > [AVG Price LY], UNICHAR(9650),UNICHAR(9660))

KPI AVG Color = IF([KPI AVG Arrow] = UNICHAR(9650), "#009900", "#FF0000")

KPI Rev Arrow = SWITCH(TRUE(), [Revenue] > [Revenue LY], UNICHAR(9650),UNICHAR(9660))

KPI Rev Color = IF([KPI Rev Arrow] = UNICHAR(9650), "#009900", "#FF0000")

KPI Volume Arrow = SWITCH(TRUE(), [Volume] > [Volume LY], UNICHAR(9650),UNICHAR(9660))

KPI Volume Color = IF([KPI Volume Arrow] = UNICHAR(9650), "#009900", "#FF0000")





Follow instructions on the GIF below



YOY Volume indicator: Repeat the process in the GIF above but (1) replace the Field with KPI Volume Arrow and (2) replace the Field Value color with KPI Volume Color measure

YOY Revenue indicator: Repeat the process in the GIF above but (1) replace the Field with KPI Revenue Arrow and (2) replace the Field Value color with KPI Revenue Color measure
